      "body" : "Before Java 7, you could also use Commons Lang&#39;s <code>ObjectUtils.toString(Object,String)</code> which is equivalent. -&gt; <a href=\"https://commons.apache.org/proper/commons-lang/javadocs/api-2.6/org/apache/commons/lang/ObjectUtils.html#toString(java.lang.Object\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">commons.apache.org/proper/commons-lang/javadocs/api-2.6/org/&zwnj;&#8203;&hellip;</a>, java.lang.String)"
